      """
      {
        "key": "rNxgJ2niG2eQkiJLWwmvHDimWVpm4L"
      }
      """
    And the current account has 1 "key"
    And I use an authentication token
    When I send a PATCH request to "/accounts/test1/keys/$0" with the following:
      """
      {
        "data": {
